C

Cache - Class in com.kamontat.model.management
This class for save the object into file and can restore every time
Easy to use and manage
call method loadCache(file name) to get name of the file cache and than there have 4 method that you can use it saveToFile(object) - must be sure that object implements Serializable. loadFromFile(class) - you can specify return class by pass in parameter. isExist() - to check that cache file is exist or not. delete() - delete cache file.
